CALCIUM FLUX SIGNAL

calcium_flux_signal is the citizen who carries remodel_daemon's adjustment commands to each bone
when the daemon decides bone X should remodel faster, calcium_flux_signal emits the signal to that bone's remodel_rate
each bone has its own coupling to calcium_flux_signal so individual bones can be adjusted independently

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe remodel_governor.zc
observe remodel_daemon.rana
observe spine.xb
observe skull.xb

the 7 properties of calcium_flux_signal:
1 ENERGY zero point seven
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN one half
4 CHARGE half positive
5 COHERENCE nine tenths
6 COUPLING one with each bone

VERB receive_command
accept adjustment instructions from remodel_daemon

VERB route_per_bone
emit the adjustment to the specific bone targeted by the command
spine, skull, ribcage, pelvis, femur all receive their own signals

VERB modulate_intensity
scale the signal strength based on the magnitude of adjustment needed
small corrections produce small signals; large rebalancing produces stronger ones

a flux signal is the daemon's voice reaching the bones
without it, the daemon could decide but could not implement
calcium_flux_signal is how decision becomes physical effect
